2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffifth-generation-jets-made-ukraine-war-russia-su-57-missing-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econspicuous%20by%20its%20absence%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20Ukraine%20war.%20This%20probably%20reflects%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-keeps-new-weapons-ukraine-fears-reputational-damage-losing-them-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efear%20of%20embarrassment%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20losing%20an%20advanced%20weapon%20%E2%80%94%20and%20perhaps%20a%20lack%20of%20confidence%20that%20the%20capabilities%20of%20these%20weapons%20won't%20match%20the%20rhetoric.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20has%20been%20hurting%20Ukraine%20over%20the%20last%20six%20months%20are%20massive%20numbers%20of%20glide%20bombs%20dropped%20by%20older%20Su-34%20and%20Su-35%20jets.%20Stealth%20fighters%20aren't%20needed%20for%20Russia's%20un-stealthy%20strategy%3A%20obliterate%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcz5drkr8l1ko%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUkrainian%20defenses%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20glide%20bombs%2C%20then%20send%20in%20poorly%20trained%20convict-infantry%20to%20mop%20up.%20It's%20a%20crude%2C%20costly%20approach%20that%20nonetheless%20has%20enabled%20Russia%20to%20capture%20some%20small%20chunks%20of%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20with%20American-made%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fukraine-get-its-first-f-16-jets-june-july-says-kyiv-military-source-2024-05-10%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EF-16%20fighters%3C%2Fa%3E%20arriving%20soon%2C%20Ukraine's%20air%20force%20probably%20can't%20drive%20off%20Russian%20jets%20lobbing%20glide%20bombs%20from%2050%20miles%20behind%20Russian%20lines%2C%20safe%20behind%20ground-based%20air%20defenses.%20Cheap%20one-way%20attack%20drones%20may%20be%20the%20next%20best%20thing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMichael%20Peck%20is%20a%20defense%20writer%20whose%20work%20has%20appeared%20in%20Forbes%2C%20Defens