%20supports%20women%20and%20girls%20through%20sports%2C%20aiming%20to%20develop%20their%20leadership%20skills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhether%20you%20come%20in%20first%20or%20last%2C%20it%20doesn't%20matter.%20You've%20done%20something%20almost%20superhuman%2C%20something%20that%200.05%25%20of%20the%20world's%20population%20will%20never%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Race%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Dau's%20journey%20was%20far%20from%20easy.%20Running%20in%20temperatures%20as%20high%20as%2035%20degrees%20Celsius%2C%20her%20shoes%20melted%2C%20and%20she%20battled%20a%20hip%20injury%20from%20the%20very%20first%20day%2C%20reports%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.straitstimes.com%2Fsport%2Fultramarathoner-natalie-dau-claims-singapore-record-with-1000km-thailand-to-s-pore-run%5C%22%3EThe%20Strait%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E.%20By%20Day%203%2C%20she%20developed%20a%20urinary%20tract%20infection.%20However%2C%20Dau's%20saw%20through%20these%20challenges.%20Each%20day%2C%20she%20covered%20at%20least%2084%20kilometres.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThroughout%20the%20run%2C%20Ms%20Dau%20kept%20her%20supporters%20updated%20through%20nightly%20voice%20messages%2C%20sharing%20both%20her%20triumphs%20and%20her%20struggles.%20Her%20team%2C%20instrumental%20in%20the%20success%2C%20provided%20essential%20support%2C%20ensuring%20safety%20and%20logistics%20were%20meticulously%20planned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDau's%20accomplishment%20extends%20beyond%20personal%20achievement.%20She%20hopes%20her%20journey%20will%20inspire%20others%2C%20particularly%20women%20and%20older%20individuals%2C%20to%20challenge%20their%20own%20limits.%20%26quot%3BWhether%20you%20come%20in%20first%20or%20last%2C%20it%20doesn't%20matter.%20You've%20done%20something%20almost%20superhuman%2C%20something%20that%200.05%25%20of%20the%20world's%20population%20will%20never%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20physical%20toll%20of%20the%20run%20was%