nd%20bowlers%20are%20not%20performing%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Afridi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%20have%20endured%20a%20dismal%202024%20T20%20World%20Cup%20campaign%2C%20losing%20their%20first%20two%20matches%20to%20co-hosts%20USA%20and%20then%20India.%20The%20abandonment%20of%20USA's%20game%20against%20Ireland%20confirmed%20Pakistan's%20group%20stage%20exit%2C%20as%20they%20can%20now%20neither%20match%20India%20nor%20USA's%20points%20tally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECriticism%20has%20come%20from%20several%20stalwarts%20of%20Pakistan%20cricket%2C%20from%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Wasim%20Akram%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F438-wasim-akram-playerprofile%5C%22%3EWasim%20Akram%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shoaib%20Akhtar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F381-shoaib-akhtar-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShoaib%20Akhtar%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Babar%20Azam's%20batting%20and%20captaincy%20has%20been%20heavily%20criticised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%20face%20Ireland%20in%20their%20final%20Group%20A%20game%20on%20Sunday%2C%20June%2016%2C%20in%20what%20will%20be%20a%20final%20chance%20for%20them%20to%20get%20some%20pride%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718509860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F80m8len8_shahid-afridi-babar-azam-instagram-afp_625x300_14_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fkids-born-during-covid-have-no-idea-pakistan-great-loses-cool-discussing-t20-world-cup-capitulation-5896844%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Afridi%20pinpointed%20poor%20performances%20and%20bad%20captaincy%20as%20the%20reasons%20for%20Pakistan's%20failure%20at%20the%202024%20T20%20World%20Cup.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fkids-born-during-covid-have-no-idea-pakistan-great-loses-cool-discussing-