20information.%20A%20scammer%20usually%20sends%20an%20email%20or%20some%20other%20message%20pretending%20to%20be%20a%20company%20or%20individual%20the%20victim%20is%20familiar%20with%2C%20asking%20for%20credit%20card%20info%2C%20passwords%2C%20or%20other%20sensitive%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20scams%20occur%20on%20sites%20like%20Facebook%20or%20Craigslist%2C%20where%20researchers%20said%20they%20found%20207%20phony%20postings%20advertising%20Ozempic%20in%20just%20one%20day%20in%20April.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Facebook%2C%20scammers%20often%20pretend%20to%20be%20doctors%2C%20claiming%20to%20hand%20out%20Ozempic%20and%20other%20drugs%20without%20a%20prescription%2C%20the%20report%20says.%20Once%20they%20contact%20potential%20victims%2C%20the%20scammers%20pressure%20them%20to%20use%20unconventional%20payment%20methods%20for%20prescription%20drugs%2C%20McAfee%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20example%20on%20Facebook%20Marketplace%20included%20a%20'Doctor%20Melissa'%20based%20in%20Canada%20who%20could%20provide%20Mounjaro%20and%20Ozempic%20without%20a%20prescription%2C%20with%20payment%20available%20through%20Bitcoin%2C%20Zelle%2C%20Venmo%2C%20and%20Cash%20App%20%E2%80%94%20all%20of%20which%20are%20non-standard%20payment%20methods%20for%20prescription%20drugs%20and%20should%20be%20red%20flags%20for%20consumers.%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20studies%20say%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbernie-sanders-ozempic-cheaper-novo-nordisk-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOzempic%20costs%20just%20%245%20to%20make%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20drug%20sells%20for%20about%20%241%2C000%20a%20month.%20This%20high%20price%20makes%20some%20consumers%20more%20eager%20to%20take%20a%20cheap%20offer%20online%2C%20McAfee%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCybercriminals%20are%20always%20on%20the%20lookout%20for%20ways%20to%20make%20their%20scams%20more%20attractive%20and%20believable%2C%26quot%3B%20Abhishek%20Karnik%2C%20