Hetal%20still%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20found%20a%20sponsor.%20Time%20was%20running%20out.%20But%2C%20as%20she%20emphasises%2C%20help%20always%20arrives%20when%20you%20least%20expect%20it.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20local%20Gujarati%20newspaper%20would%20often%20write%20about%20my%20achievements%2C%20and%20when%20I%20approached%20them%20with%20this%20dilemma%2C%20they%20put%20out%20an%20article%20asking%20if%20anyone%20would%20like%20to%20sponsor%20me%20to%20participate%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F193355%2Fnational-sports-day-pv-sindhu-greatest-moments-sports-india-history%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20tournament%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20many%20came%20forward%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98I%20was%20celebrated%20for%20my%20strength%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20a%20teenager%2C%20the%20memory%20of%20standing%20on%20foreign%20ground%20when%20she%20landed%20in%20Estonia%20is%20still%20fresh%20in%20Hetal%E2%80%99s%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20aware%20that%20no%20one%20from%20India%20would%20be%20there%20at%20the%20tournament%20and%20was%20nervous.%20Here%20I%20was%2C%20going%20for%20something%20that%20was%20so%20new%2C%20and%20in%20a%20strange%20place.%20While%20I%20managed%20to%20find%20a%20sponsor%2C%20the%20funds%20were%20limited%2C%20and%20I%20had%20to%20be%20extremely%20careful%20about%20budgeting.%20But%20while%20the%20fear%20of%20it%20all%20set%20in%2C%20so%20did%20luck%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20mayor%20of%20the%20town%20came%20personally%20to%20receive%20me%20at%20the%20airport%20and%20shared%20how%20happy%20he%20was%20that%20someone%20from%20India%20was%20participating.%20The%20organisers%20saw%20to%20it%20that%20my%20vegetarian%20food%20preferences%20were%20taken%20care%20of%20and%20that%20a%20representative%20accompanied%20me%20at%20all%20times