%2C%20%E2%80%9CThink%20of%20our%20platform%20as%20a%20doctor%20for%20water%20infrastructure%2C%20telling%20buildings%20what%E2%80%99s%20wrong%20with%20their%20infrastructure%20and%20what%20it%20needs%2C%20as%20well%20as%20providing%20the%20medicine%20to%20fix%20it%2C%20whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20directing%20technicians%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F344518%2Ffind-missing-children-raju-nepali-duars-express-mail-ngo-rescues-trafficked-children-counselling%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWhatsApp%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20the%20right%20amount%20of%20chemical%20dosage%20required%2C%20automating%20equipment%20to%20function%20properly%20or%20directing%20operators%20on%20the%20best%20next%20steps.%20Through%20our%20work%2C%20we%20help%20clients%20save%20crores%20in%20fines%2C%20but%20more%20importantly%2C%20they%20recycle%20their%20wastewater%20%E2%80%94%2090%20million%20litres%20of%20wastewater%20is%20treated%20daily%20at%20plants%20associated%20with%20us.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20present%2C%20over%2040%20industry%20giants%2C%20including%20Tata%20Power%2C%20Delhi%20Jal%20Board%2C%20Britannia%2C%20and%20Leela%20Hotels%2C%20are%20using%20the%20Gurugram-based%20startup%E2%80%99s%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FSnapinsta.app_434552169_933189761637726_8367049811662365564_n_1080-1718112498.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22How%20do%20you%20treat%20water%20Digital%20Paani%20style%3F%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FSnapinsta.app_434552169_933189761637726_8367049811662365564_n_1080-1718112498.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FSnapinsta.app_434552169_933189761637726_836