pish.%20%E2%80%9COnce%2C%20one%20of%20my%20teachers%20came%20to%20our%20home%20and%20straight%20away%20went%20to%20complain%20to%20my%20%3Cem%3Ebaba%20%3C%2Fem%3E(father).%20He%20said%20if%20I%20ever%20became%20serious%20about%20my%20studies%2C%20he%20would%20shave%20his%20moustache%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20laughs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrowing%20up%2C%20Aaditya%20went%20on%20to%20pursue%20electronics%20engineering%20from%20Lovely%20Professional%20University%2C%20Punjab%2C%20and%20later%20on%20pursued%20higher%20education%20in%20business%20administration%20from%20IIT%20Roorkee.%20After%20working%20for%20two%20years%20in%20a%20private%20bank%2C%20he%20eventually%20quit%20his%20job%20to%20prepare%20for%20UPSC%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20shaped%20his%20vision%20was%20a%20conversation%20with%20a%20bureaucrat%20at%20IIT%20Roorkee.%20%E2%80%9CComing%20from%20Bihar%2C%20I%20knew%20the%20charm%20that%20comes%20with%20being%20an%20IAS%20officer.%20But%20you%20cannot%20delve%20into%20the%20service%20just%20because%20of%20the%20charm.%20I%20was%20inspired%20to%20become%20an%20IAS%20after%20speaking%20to%20a%20bureaucrat%20who%20was%20working%20with%20the%20railway%20services.%20I%20learned%20about%20the%20ins%20and%20outs%20of%20UPSC%20from%20him%20and%20my%20peers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20him%20two%20failed%20attempts%20to%20finally%20clear%20UPSC%20CSE%20in%20the%202022%20examination%20with%20an%20impressive%20All%20India%20Rank%20of%2048.%20Currently%2C%20he%20is%20posted%20as%20an%20assistant%20collector%20in%20Ranchi%2C%20Jharkhand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCt689mSPpct%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCt689mSPpct%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%2