o%20breach%20the%20river%20banks%20nor%20did%20it%20render%20the%20inhabitants%20of%C2%A0Jharkhali%20homeless%20despite%20it%20being%20a%20low-lying%20area.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20same%20was%20not%20the%20case%20elsewhere%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20Matla%2C%20Bidyadhari%20and%20Herobhanga%20rivers%20surrounding%20Jharkhali%20with%20a%20radius%20of%203-6%20km%2C%20the%20area%20is%20cyclone-prone.%20The%20villagers%20here%20have%20previously%20witnessed%20cyclones%20including%20Aila%20(May%202009)%2C%20Fani%20(May%202019)%2C%20Bulbul%20(November%202019)%20and%20Amphan%20(May%202020).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Ranjan%20Mondol%2C%20a%20former%20gram%20%3Cem%3Epradhan%20%3C%2Fem%3E(head)%2C%20around%205%2C00%2C000%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F253954%2Fs-sathish-forest-range-officer-tamil-nadu-wildlife-marine-mangroves-olive-ridley-turtle-poaching-underwater-clean-plastic-national-park-international-ranger-award-2021-switzerland-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emangrove%20saplings%20have%20been%20planted%20here%20%3C%2Fa%3Eover%20the%20years%20covering%20100%20hectares%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20efforts%20of%20both%20the%20JSB%2C%20and%20the%20forest%20department.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20contributed%20to%20Jharkhali%20coming%20out%20relatively%20better%20than%20most%20other%20places%2C%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20985px)%20100vw%2C%20985px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FWoemn-of-Jharkali_11zon-1717770498.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22985%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20hardworking%20women%20of%20Jharkhali.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FWoemn-of-Jharkali_11zon-1717770498.jpg%20985w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fup