ty%20of%20the%20packaging%20is%20paper%2C%20this%20lamination%20makes%20them%20unfit%20to%20recycle%20or%20biodegrade%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Khushboo%20Gandhi%2C%20founder%20of%20Pune-based%20startup%20%E2%80%98Go%20Do%20Good%E2%80%99%20that%20develops%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F311118%2Fpernod-richard-one-for-our-planet-initiative-encourages-sustainable-packaging-to-avoid-pollution%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esustainable%20packaging%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSimilarly%2C%20the%20black%20ink%2C%20which%20is%20commonly%20used%20in%20printing%20newspapers%20and%20magazines%2C%20has%20carbon%20in%20it.%20It%20cannot%20go%20back%20to%20the%20planet%20without%20proper%20processing%20because%20it%20is%20full%20of%20heavy%20metals%20and%20chemicals%20that%20will%20affect%20the%20soil%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fgo-do-good-startup-2-1717687958.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Khushboo%20says%20these%20products%20are%20equally%20durable%20and%20keep%20items%20like%20powder%2C%20liquid%20detergent%2C%20and%20food%20items%20safe.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fgo-do-good-startup-2-1717687958.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fgo-do-good-startup-2-1717687958-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fgo-do-good-startup-2-1717687958-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fgo-do-good-startup-2-1717687958-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fgo-do-good-startup-2-1717687958-150x79.jpg%2015